            <note xml:id="foot.f2"><ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_7952.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> 2d ed.</ref> was published in February 1876 (<hi rend="italic">Publisher’s circular</hi> 1876). CD’s publisher was John Murray.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">See <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_7661.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Tegetmeier 1867</ref>, p. 287.</note>
